channel.title: CVE Feed for SAP SE -- SAP 3D Visual Enterprise Viewer
channel.description: The latest CVEs for SAP SE -- SAP 3D Visual Enterprise Viewer

item.title: CVE-2020-6375|2024-08-04T09:02:40.215Z -- sap%20se -- sap%203d%20visual%20enterprise%20viewer
item.description: SAP 3D Visual Enterprise Viewer, version - 9, allows a user to open manipulated Right Computer Graphics Metafile (.cgm) file received from untrusted sources which results in crashing of the application and becoming temporarily unavailable until the user restarts the application, this is caused due to Improper Input Validation.
